reviewText: I am a special education teacher who used this video as an attention grabber in my lesson. The kids still request it!
I work at a hospital and our infection control says to wash hands for a minimum 15 secs.  I think the DVD is great!
Very good and age appropriate.  Only reason not 5 stars is "soapy" says to wash hands for 10-15 seconds when new material says 20 seconds (singing the birthday song twice)
